    {
      "name": "create_raffle",
      "docs": [
        "Create a product raffle. The prize (a TV, a gift card, etc.) lives",
        "off-chain; this account holds the ticket money + the rules.",
        "",
        "`max_entries` bounds the number of *unique* buyers (the account is",
        "sized up front), which keeps the on-chain vec from blowing past",
        "Solana's account size limits. Repeat purchases by the same wallet are",
        "merged into one entry, so 10k tickets across 300 wallets = 300 entries."
      ],
      "discriminator": [
