    {
      "name": "draw_winner",
      "docs": [
        "End the raffle. Callable by the authority once the deadline has passed,",
        "or early once all tickets are sold.",
        "",
        "- If `tickets_sold >= min_tickets`: pick a weighted-random winner,",
        "send proceeds (minus fee) to the payout recipient and the fee to the",
        "fee recipient. The winner is recorded on-chain for off-chain",
        "fulfillment of the physical/digital prize.",
        "- Otherwise: the raffle failed to hit its floor -> flip to `Refunding`",
        "so every buyer can reclaim their SOL.",
        "",
        "RANDOMNESS NOTE: this uses the SlotHashes sysvar as an entropy source,",
        "which is good enough for a devnet demo but is theoretically",
        "influenceable by a colluding leader. For mainnet, swap `derive_random`",
        "for a Switchboard On-Demand / VRF callback."
      ],
