    {
      "name": "reclaim_prize",
      "docs": [
        "Operator reclaims the escrowed SOL prize from a raffle that FAILED its",
        "floor (status `Refunding`). Buyers still reclaim their ticket money",
        "separately via `claim_refund`, so the status stays `Refunding` — this",
        "only returns the operator's escrowed prize. Permissionless, but the",
        "prize can only ever go back to the recorded `authority` (so a keeper can",
        "run it), and only once (guarded by `prize_delivered`)."
      ],
